There's probably some generalization refactoring we could do to make such a `\vdots` menu a general component, but I'm not going to block this PR on that.', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2022, 10, 7, 22, 51, 22, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'timabbott', 'type': 'User'}]
